title: LF Flex Team | I'm Silver 2
body:
Have heaps of spare time so I'm looking for a flex team / people to play flex with, not too serious but not trolling either ;)

My strongest champions are:

Mid | Azir, Corki, Fiora, Twisted Fate, Lulu, Lux, Diana
Bot | Jinx, Caitlyn, Lucian, MF
Support | Nami, Janna, Brand

Not too confident with top or jungle

If this CV interests you, hmu :)
